name: Moonwell Flagship USDC (Morpho Vault)
description: Moonwell Flagship USDC Morpho Vault is a one-token deposit vault curated by B.Protocol and Block Analitica. It is intended to optimize risk-adjusted interest earned from blue-chip collateral markets on Morpho Blue protocol on Base network. Morpho Vaults are curated lending vaults allocating deposits to listed markets. Each vault is customizable and has a different risk profile. Curators are independent, third-party risk experts who use their expertise to offer various Morpho Vaults.
